  "version": "1.0.0",
  "description": "Beatbox (10) × 4 articulations + Shaker + Conga. Synthetic electronic feel, tempo=128, tight GATHER=0.9. The human beatboxer studied by a machine and improved — then studied by a human again.",
  "tags": [
    "aether",
    "beatbox",
    "electronic",
    "synthetic",
    "machine",
    "transcendental"
